-ROUGH GREASE DUCT WORK (MODIFICATION NO. PS14); 
-MISSING FOOD SERVICE EQUIPMENT (FSE) REPLACEMENT (MODIFICATION  NO. PS21);
-BANQUETTE SEATING INSTALLATION.
